{"tid":2079321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"初選投票策略：一拖十 送最多抗爭派入去做重光派候選人","createTime":"2020-06-25T17:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T09:03:32.000Z","uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"99d2ab8b708bfdddf8f2839ac062b7c9c1fc0bd8","tid":2079321,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T17:16:25.000Z","msg":"其實初選個玩法係多議席單票制<br />\n而要達到目的 即係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">送最多抗爭派</span></span></strong>入去做重光派(民主+本土派)候選人<br />\n就要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">平均地令抗爭派高票</span></span></strong><br />\n唔可以堆晒啲票落一個人到 (例子：2016新西heidi)<br />\n<br />\n根據目標議席數66443+3 (進取者會話係76443+4)<br />\n新東6/7，新西6，九西4，港島4，九東3，超區3/4<br />\n<br />\n點樣定義係咪抗爭派候選人呢<br />\n可以睇番邊個簽咗墨落無悔抗爭派立場書<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">以下例子拋磚引玉</span></strong></ins><br />\n新東應該<ins><strong>7個朋友一組</strong></ins>：一人投一個抗爭派<br />\n1/陳志全<br />\n2/劉頴匡<br />\n3/何桂藍<br />\n4/鄒家成<br />\n5/柯耀林<br />\n6/范國威<br />\n7/呂智恆<br />\n8/楊岳橋 (如果有第8個朋友)<br />\n<br />\n新西應該<ins><strong>7個朋友一組</strong></ins>：一人投一個抗爭派<br />\n1/朱凱廸<br />\n2/吳敏兒<br />\n3/伍健偉<br />\n4/張可森<br />\n5/黃子悅<br />\n6/郭家麒<br />\n7/譚凱邦<br />\n<br />\n九西應該<ins><strong>4個朋友一組</strong></ins>：一人投一個抗爭派<br />\n因為九西未定出選名單數目，但其實<ins>最多都係拎得4個位</ins>，所以應該要投4個最具抗爭實力嘅人<br />\n1/張崑陽<br />\n2/何啟明<br />\n3/劉偉聰 (5個中年紀最大)<br />\n4/馮達浚<br />\n5/劉澤鋒<br />\n<br />\n港島應該<ins><strong>4個朋友一組</strong></ins>：一人投一個抗爭派<br />\n因為港島未定出選名單數目，但其實<ins>最多都係拎得4個位</ins>，所以應該要投4個最具抗爭實力嘅人<br />\n1/羅冠聰<br />\n2/袁嘉蔚<br />\n3/鄭達鴻<br />\n4/楊雪盈 (同時為灣仔區議會主席)<br />\n5/梁晃維<br />\n6/彭卓棋<br />\n<br />\n九東應該<ins><strong>4個朋友一組</strong></ins>：一人投一個抗爭派<br />\n雖然九東定左出5條名單，但係人都知<ins>最多都係拎得3個位</ins>，所以應該要投3個最具抗爭實力嘅人<br />\n1/黃之鋒<br />\n2/譚文豪<br />\n3/李嘉達<br />\n4/譚得志<br />\n5/施德來"},{"pid":"260bfb2f87de742b7b7c2320f63a398ad5eba8da","tid":2079321,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T17:18:03.000Z","msg":"慳返啖氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0575014fe46a18ff7a9700501fcf347284dc2a","tid":2079321,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"260bfb2f87de742b7b7c2320f63a398ad5eba8da","tid":2079321,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T17:18:03.000Z","msg":"慳返啖氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T17:22:30.000Z","msg":"#343361 有咩睪見"},{"pid":"f4f4987df8e9c88a3871366b30435bb858d184a0","tid":2079321,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e0575014fe46a18ff7a9700501fcf347284dc2a","tid":2079321,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"260bfb2f87de742b7b7c2320f63a398ad5eba8da","tid":2079321,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T17:18:03.000Z","msg":"慳返啖氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T17:22:30.000Z","msg":"#343361 有咩睪見"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T17:26:23.000Z","msg":"#177955 投素人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9314ab4d0a29ca6d3863646776b541776724352","tid":2079321,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4f4987df8e9c88a3871366b30435bb858d184a0","tid":2079321,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e0575014fe46a18ff7a9700501fcf347284dc2a","tid":2079321,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"260bfb2f87de742b7b7c2320f63a398ad5eba8da","tid":2079321,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T17:18:03.000Z","msg":"慳返啖氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T17:22:30.000Z","msg":"#343361 有咩睪見"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T17:26:23.000Z","msg":"#177955 投素人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"re